cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite it as below."
type: dataset
title: "Polymarket Resolution Typology Dataset"
abstract: >
  A three-class classification of 911,237 Polymarket prediction markets by resolution
  mechanism (deadline_resolved, event_resolved, unclassifiable), released as a
  methodological resource for ILS-based informed-trading research and related
  studies of prediction-market structure. Snapshot cutoff: 2026-04-27.
authors:
